    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551550/extras/c239933812fd4b2b349a375175bad00e.avif?t=1749380883\" width=616 height=72 /></span>自从菲拉娜救了莉莉一命后，两人在乡村过着平静的生活。某天，当菲拉娜回家时却发现莉莉倒在地板上。散落在她身边的是稀有的炼金材料，各种关于圣灵药的理论资料，和一些其他的炼金用品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >菲拉娜惊讶地问莉莉这是什么情况，莉莉说她一直在和一种绝症抗争，但只有圣灵药才能药到病除。但是她现在已无力继续寻找剩下的材料，于是菲拉娜主动请缨代为效劳。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在莉莉勉强接受了菲拉娜的提议后，菲拉娜来到附近的城镇住下，准备搜集剩下的材料的信息。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >菲拉娜能否成功得到莉莉需要的材料呢？是什么样的神秘集团也在搜集这些材料？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这一切的答案将由你来揭晓！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551550/extras/be3e07ab96ff2989463cf0269f12c3bb.avif?t=1749380883\" width=616 height=73 /></span>在这个经典的回合制战斗角色扮演游戏中，你将前往各种地区搜集需要材料。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一个法师，菲拉娜随着等级提升能学到各种新的技能用以克敌制胜。在旅途中她也能学会一些极具冲击性的技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而你败北的次数将导致不同的剧情走向。尝试找出所有的结局吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551550/extras/11228b6f3e42ee5d83771371a83d33d8.avif?t=1749380883\" width=616 height=73 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551550/extras/990b2676e529f685b1e0ded2c3a144ea.avif?t=1749380883\" width=616 height=275 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551550/extras/62d2d34af5aa5326aa7dbcd4dc5f2b03.avif?t=1749380883\" width=616 height=275 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551550/extras/c3d0c902661f3b0d3abf90ce8cddab1d.avif?t=1749380883\" width=616 height=73 /></span><strong>探索内容丰富</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以自由探索城镇附近的广袤区域，每个区域都有各种独特的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>精彩纷呈的任务</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然村民安居乐业，但也依然需要各种各样的帮助。游戏设置有多个支线任务，完成它们可以得到丰厚的奖励！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>富有深度的剧情</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她们和家人的遭遇远不止目前所见所闻，曾经辉煌的家族也各自有着错综复杂的过去。而这一切将由你步步揭晓！</p>",
